```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant CMD as Command Service
  participant WDB as Write DB
  participant BUS as Event Bus
  participant PROJ as Projector
  participant RDB as Read DB
  participant QRY as Query Service

  C->>CMD: POST /orders (command)
  CMD->>CMD: Validate invariants
  CMD->>WDB: Insert Order (transaction)
  CMD->>BUS: Publish OrderCreated (event_id)
  CMD-->>C: 202 Accepted (eventual consistency)

  BUS-->>PROJ: Deliver OrderCreated
  PROJ->>PROJ: Idempotency check (event_id)
  PROJ->>RDB: Upsert read model row(s)

  C->>QRY: GET /orders/{id}
  QRY->>RDB: Read projection
  QRY-->>C: 200 OK (may be stale until projection catches up)
```
